  "title": "feat(analytics): Push pagination",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for submitting a pull request!\r\n  Please provide enough information so that others can review your pull request.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Summary**\r\n\r\nCurrently the analytics widget doesn't trigger `pushFunction` during pagination. This PR adds a parameter to allow the `pushFunction` to be triggered there.\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\n`pushFunction` can be triggered on pagination 🎉 \r\n",
